  User Query:           give me a list of all AI engineers
  Generated Sql:        SELECT c.*, a.id AS application_id
FROM candidates c
INNER JOIN applications a ON a.candidate_id = c.id
WHERE a.applied_position ~* '\mAI\M' OR a.applied_position ILIKE '%artificial intelligence%'
ORDER BY c.created_at DESC
LIMIT 20
  Explanation:          List candidates with applied positions matching AI or artificial intelligence, ordered by creation date.

